---
/**
 * @fileoverview Force light theme utility to prevent dark mode.
 *
 * Forces light mode only. Prevents respecting system dark mode preference.
 * Uses meta tag approach to set theme BEFORE page render (flash prevention).
 *
 * Include this in <head> to ensure light-only theme.
 *
 * @module components/utilities/ForceLightTheme
 *
 * @example
 * ```astro
 * <head>
 *   <ForceLightTheme />
 * </head>
 * ```
 *
 * @author How To Win Capitalism Team
 * @since 1.0.0
 */
---

<meta name="color-scheme" content="light" />
<script is:inline>
  // Set theme immediately before any rendering
  document.documentElement.dataset.theme = 'light';
</script>
